number one in anything else

1412
01:27:10,770 --> 01:27:13,530
I only want you to be number one in mahjong

1413
01:27:14,370 --> 01:27:17,070
Since I'm such an embarassment
to you, I'll leave

1414
01:27:17,410 --> 01:27:18,900
You're leaving…

1415
01:27:18,980 --> 01:27:21,810
Who's gonna take photo
with me later when I win?

1416
01:27:22,680 --> 01:27:25,170
