1427
01:28:05,760 --> 01:28:07,750
You can do it if you put your heart into it

1428
01:28:07,820 --> 01:28:09,590
Chicken Hand is also considered a win

1429
01:28:09,660 --> 01:28:12,130
Don't be afraid of losing just do it

1430
01:28:19,670 --> 01:28:20,690
Brother

1431
