1432
01:28:24,210 --> 01:28:27,640
From now on, you'll have to call me
the King of Mahjong for 11 consecutive years

1433
01:28:28,210 --> 01:28:31,200
Did you eat a lot of
garlic? Your mouth stinks

1434
01:28:31,310 --> 01:28:32,750
