into competition

1530
01:33:18,930 --> 01:33:20,090
after all these years

1531
01:33:20,170 --> 01:33:21,640
Of course I'm happy

1532
01:33:21,740 --> 01:33:23,260
Are you?

1533
01:33:23,340 --> 01:33:26,000
