01:36:45,410 --> 01:36:46,500
Seven Character

1591
01:36:46,880 --> 01:36:48,100
Five Circles

1592
01:36:48,180 --> 01:36:49,840
- In-between - Pong

1593
01:36:55,620 --> 01:36:57,020
Three Bamboos

1594
01:36:57,150 --> 01:36:58,480
I'll take that

1595
01:37:01,320 --> 01:37:02,020
Eight Circles

1596
01:37:02,160 --> 01:37:03,620
- In-between - I'll take that

1597
01:37:03,730 --> 01:37:07,390
Flowerless, Concealed, Sequence Hand
win with a single Eight Circles, three points

1598
01:37:09,870 --> 01:37:10,990
