01:37:29,890 --> 01:37:31,380
Six Character

1603
01:37:33,060 --> 01:37:35,180
- Two Circles - I'll take that

1604
01:37:40,900 --> 01:37:42,660
- Three Bamboos - Pong

1605
01:37:48,670 --> 01:37:50,660
