01:38:06,560 --> 01:38:10,220
One has polio, one s pea-brained

1611
01:38:10,330 --> 01:38:11,790
Just play

1612
01:38:16,900 --> 01:38:18,870
- Eight Character - Pong

1613
01:38:21,470 --> 01:38:22,870
win

